###**Dr. Jianghao WANG (王江浩)** , Assistant Professor
> State Key Laboratory of Resources & Environmental Information System, 
> Institute of Geographical Sciences and Natural Resources Research,  
> Chinese Academy of Sciences,  
> A 11, Datun Road, Anwai,  
> Beijing, 100101, China
> Email: [wangjh@lreis.ac.cn](mailto:wangjh@lreis.ac.cn)


## EDUCATION
- **Ph.D:** [Institute of Geographic Sciences & Natural Resources Research](http://english.igsnrr.cas.cn/), Chinese Academy of Sciences, China (Supervised by Prof. [Chenhu Zhou](http://sourcedb.igsnrr.cas.cn/zw/zjrck/200906/t20090626_1842630.html), Academician of CAS; [Prof. Yong Ge](http://sourcedb.igsnrr.cas.cn/zw/zjrck/200910/t20091026_2590290.html); and [Prof. Gerard B.M. Heuvelink](https://www.wageningenur.nl/en/Persons/Gerard-dr.ir.-GBM-Gerard-Heuvelink.htm))
- **M.Sc:** [Institute of Geographic Sciences & Natural Resources Research](http://english.igsnrr.cas.cn/), Chinese Academy of Sciences, China ([Prof. Yong Ge](http://sourcedb.igsnrr.cas.cn/zw/zjrck/200910/t20091026_2590290.html))
- **B.Sc:**   [Hohai University](http://en.hhu.edu.cn/), China

## EMPLOYMENT 
- Assistant Professor in [State Key Laboratory of Resources & Environmental Information System](http://www.lreis.ac.cn), [Institute of Geographic Sciences & Natural Resources Research](http://english.igsnrr.cas.cn/), [Chinese Academy of Sciences](http://english.cas.cn/), China; 
- Associate directors of [Beijing City Lab](http://www.beijingcitylab.com/), China

## GRANTS
- 2016-2020, Co-Investigator, “**Key Theory and Method for Validation of Land Surface Remote Sensing Products**”, the Key Program of the National Natural Science Foundation of China (No. 41531174), PI: Prof Shaomin Liu.
- 2015-2020, Co-Investigator, “**Spatio-temporal Big Data Analysis**”, Science Fund for Creative Research Groups of the National Natural Science Foundation of China (No. 41421001), PI: Prof Academician Chenhu Zhou.
- 2016-2017, Principle-Investigator, “**Research on Human Mobility Pattern in Multiple Spatial Scales Through Geotagged Social Media Network**”, Open Research Fund Program of Shenzhen Key Laboratory of Spatial Smart Sensing and Services, Shenzhen University.
- 2015-2017, Principle-Investigator, “**Spatio-Temporal Mapping by Integrating Geographic Knowledge**”, LREIS, Chinese Academy of Sciences
- 2012-2015, Co-Investigator, “**Key Techniques for the Validation of Remote Sensing Products**”, National High Technology Research and Development Program of China, PI: Prof Xin Li.
- 2012-2016, Co-Investigator, “**Resources & Environmental Monitoring and Ecological Value Assessment for Impoverished Region in China**”, National Science & Technology Support Program, PI: Prof Yong Ge.
- 2012-2016, Co-Investigator, “**Monitoring Network Design for China's Floating Population**”, National Science & Technology Support Program, PI: Prof Xiaohuan Yang. 


